# User simplicity

Regular users see **plain language only** in GET_STARTED, USER_GUIDE, Start-AethelOS.bat, and the top of README.

## Never put in user docs

docker, cloudflared, cloudflare, compose, nginx, pnpm, bootstrap, relay operators

## Where infrastructure belongs

- [docs/PUBLISHER.md](docs/PUBLISHER.md) — deploy, CI, permanent URLs
- [docs/RELAY_OPERATORS.md](docs/RELAY_OPERATORS.md) — relay hosting
- README below "## Quick start" — developer clone/build

## Product path

1. Double-click Start-AethelOS.bat (or open publisher link)
2. Share link in Connection tab
3. Start community → share invite link

Docker is CI/publisher only (`-Mode Docker`, `publisher-deploy.ps1`, `AETHELOS_USE_DOCKER=1`).

Before release: `pnpm verify:release`
